  "title": "Ralph Langner: Cracking Stuxnet, a 21st-century cyber weapon",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 18259.0,
      "text": "The idea behind the Stuxnet computer worm"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18260.0,
      "end_time": 20260.0,
      "text": "is actually quite simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20260.0,
      "end_time": 23260.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t want Iran to get the bomb."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23260.0,
      "end_time": 26260.0,
      "text": "Their major asset for developing nuclear weapons"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26260.0,
      "end_time": 30260.0,
      "text": "is the Natanz uranium enrichment facility."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30260.0,
      "end_time": 32260.0,
      "text": "The gray boxes that you see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32259.0,
      "end_time": 35260.0,
      "text": "these are real-time control systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35260.0,
      "end_time": 38260.0,
      "text": "Now if we manage to compromise these systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38260.0,
      "end_time": 41260.0,
      "text": "that control drive speeds and valves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 41260.0,
      "end_time": 44260.0,
      "text": "we can actually cause a lot of problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 44260.0,
      "end_time": 46260.0,
      "text": "with the centrifuge."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46260.0,
      "end_time": 48260.0,
      "text": "The gray boxes don&#39;t run Windows software;"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48260.0,
      "end_time": 51260.0,
      "text": "they are a completely different technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51260.0,
      "end_time": 53260.0,
      "text": "But if we manage"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53260.0,
      "end_time": 56260.0,
      "text": "to place a good Windows virus"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56260.0,
      "end_time": 58260.0,
      "text": "on a notebook"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58260.0,
      "end_time": 60260.0,
      "text": "that is used by a maintenance engineer"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 60260.0,
      "end_time": 63260.0,
      "text": "to configure this gray box,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 63260.0,
      "end_time": 65259.0,
      "text": "then we are in business."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 68260.0,
      "text": "And this is the plot behind Stuxnet."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 68260.0,
      "end_time": 73260.0,
      "text": "So we start with a Windows dropper."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 73260.0,
      "end_time": 76260.0,
      "text": "The payload goes onto the gray box,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 76260.0,
      "end_time": 78260.0,
      "text": "damages the centrifuge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 78260.0,
      "end_time": 80260.0,
      "text": "and the Iranian nuclear program is delayed --"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 80260.0,
      "end_time": 82260.0,
      "text": "mission accomplished."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 82260.0,
      "end_time": 84260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s easy, huh?"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 84260.0,
      "end_time": 87260.0,
      "text": "I want to tell you how we found that out."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 87260.0,
      "end_time": 90260.0,
      "text": "When we started our research on Stuxnet six months ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 90260.0,
      "end_time": 93260.0,
      "text": "it was completely unknown what the purpose of this thing was."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 93260.0,
      "end_time": 95260.0,
      "text": "The only thing that was known"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 95260.0,
      "end_time": 98260.0,
      "text": "is it&#39;s very, very complex on the Windows part, the dropper part,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 98260.0,
      "end_time": 101260.0,
      "text": "used multiple zero-day vulnerabilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 101260.0,
      "end_time": 104260.0,
      "text": "And it seemed to want to do something"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 104260.0,
      "end_time": 106260.0,
      "text": "with these gray boxes, these real-time control systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 106260.0,
      "end_time": 108260.0,
      "text": "So that got our attention,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 108260.0,
      "end_time": 110260.0,
      "text": "and we started a lab project"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 110260.0,
      "end_time": 114260.0,
      "text": "where we infected our environment with Stuxnet"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 114260.0,
      "end_time": 116260.0,
      "text": "and checked this thing out."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 116260.0,
      "end_time": 119260.0,
      "text": "And then some very funny things happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 119260.0,
      "end_time": 122260.0,
      "text": "Stuxnet behaved like a lab rat"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 122260.0,
      "end_time": 125260.0,
      "text": "that didn&#39;t like our cheese --"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 125260.0,
      "end_time": 127260.0,
      "text": "sniffed, but didn&#39;t want to eat."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 127260.0,
      "end_time": 129259.0,
      "text": "Didn&#39;t make sense to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 129258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132260.0,
      "text": "And after we experimented with different flavors of cheese,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 132260.0,
      "end_time": 136260.0,
      "text": "I realized, well, this is a directed attack."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 136260.0,
      "end_time": 138260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s completely directed."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 138260.0,
      "end_time": 140260.0,
      "text": "The dropper is prowling actively"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 140260.0,
      "end_time": 142260.0,
      "text": "on the gray box"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 142260.0,
      "end_time": 145260.0,
      "text": "if a specific configuration is found,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 145260.0,
      "end_time": 149260.0,
      "text": "and even if the actual program code that it&#39;s trying to infect"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 149260.0,
      "end_time": 151260.0,
      "text": "is actually running on that target."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 151260.0,
      "end_time": 154260.0,
      "text": "And if not, Stuxnet does nothing."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 154260.0,
      "end_time": 156260.0,
      "text": "So that really got my attention,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 156260.0,
      "end_time": 158260.0,
      "text": "and we started to work on this"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 158260.0,
      "end_time": 160260.0,
      "text": "nearly around the clock,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 160260.0,
      "end_time": 163260.0,
      "text": "because I thought, \"Well, we don&#39;t know what the target is."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 163260.0,
      "end_time": 165260.0,
      "text": "It could be, let&#39;s say for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 165260.0,
      "end_time": 167260.0,
      "text": "a U.S. power plant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 167260.0,
      "end_time": 169260.0,
      "text": "or a chemical plant in Germany."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 169260.0,
      "end_time": 172260.0,
      "text": "So we better find out what the target is soon.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 172260.0,
      "end_time": 174260.0,
      "text": "So we extracted and decompiled"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 174260.0,
      "end_time": 176260.0,
      "text": "the attack code,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 176260.0,
      "end_time": 179260.0,
      "text": "and we discovered that it&#39;s structured in two digital bombs --"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 179260.0,
      "end_time": 182260.0,
      "text": "a smaller one and a bigger one."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 182260.0,
      "end_time": 186260.0,
      "text": "And we also saw that they are very professionally engineered"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 186260.0,
      "end_time": 190260.0,
      "text": "by people who obviously had all insider information."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 190260.0,
      "end_time": 192260.0,
      "text": "They knew all the bits and bites"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 192260.0,
      "end_time": 194260.0,
      "text": "that they had to attack."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 194260.0,
      "end_time": 197260.0,
      "text": "They probably even know the shoe size of the operator."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 197260.0,
      "end_time": 199260.0,
      "text": "So they know everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 199260.0,
      "end_time": 202260.0,
      "text": "And if you have heard that the dropper of Stuxnet"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 202260.0,
      "end_time": 204260.0,
      "text": "is complex and high-tech,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 204260.0,
      "end_time": 206260.0,
      "text": "let me tell you this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 206260.0,
      "end_time": 208260.0,
      "text": "the payload is rocket science."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 208260.0,
      "end_time": 210260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s way above everything"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 210260.0,
      "end_time": 213260.0,
      "text": "that we have ever seen before."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 213260.0,
      "end_time": 216260.0,
      "text": "Here you see a sample of this actual attack code."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 216260.0,
      "end_time": 218260.0,
      "text": "We are talking about --"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 218260.0,
      "end_time": 221260.0,
      "text": "around about 15,000 lines of code."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 221260.0,
      "end_time": 224260.0,
      "text": "Looks pretty much like old-style assembly language."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 224260.0,
      "end_time": 226260.0,
      "text": "And I want to tell you how we were able"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 226260.0,
      "end_time": 228260.0,
      "text": "to make sense out of this code."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 228260.0,
      "end_time": 231260.0,
      "text": "So what we were looking for is, first of all, system function calls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 231260.0,
      "end_time": 233260.0,
      "text": "because we know what they do."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 233260.0,
      "end_time": 237260.0,
      "text": "And then we were looking for timers and data structures"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 237260.0,
      "end_time": 239260.0,
      "text": "and trying to relate them to the real world --"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 239260.0,
      "end_time": 241260.0,
      "text": "to potential real world targets."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 241260.0,
      "end_time": 244260.0,
      "text": "So we do need target theories"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 244260.0,
      "end_time": 247260.0,
      "text": "that we can prove or disprove."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 247260.0,
      "end_time": 249260.0,
      "text": "In order to get target theories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 249260.0,
      "end_time": 251260.0,
      "text": "we remember"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 251260.0,
      "end_time": 253260.0,
      "text": "that it&#39;s definitely hardcore sabotage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 253260.0,
      "end_time": 255260.0,
      "text": "it must be a high-value target"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 255260.0,
      "end_time": 258260.0,
      "text": "and it is most likely located in Iran,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 258260.0,
      "end_time": 262260.0,
      "text": "because that&#39;s where most of the infections had been reported."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 262260.0,
      "end_time": 265260.0,
      "text": "Now you don&#39;t find several thousand targets in that area."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 265260.0,
      "end_time": 267260.0,
      "text": "It basically boils down"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 267260.0,
      "end_time": 269260.0,
      "text": "to the Bushehr nuclear power plant"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 269260.0,
      "end_time": 271260.0,
      "text": "and to the Natanz fuel enrichment plant."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 271260.0,
      "end_time": 273260.0,
      "text": "So I told my assistant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 273260.0,
      "end_time": 276260.0,
      "text": "\"Get me a list of all centrifuge and power plant experts from our client base.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 276260.0,
      "end_time": 278260.0,
      "text": "And I phoned them up and picked their brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 278260.0,
      "end_time": 280260.0,
      "text": "in an effort to match their expertise"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 280260.0,
      "end_time": 283260.0,
      "text": "with what we found in code and data."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 283260.0,
      "end_time": 285260.0,
      "text": "And that worked pretty well."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 285260.0,
      "end_time": 287260.0,
      "text": "So we were able to associate"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 287260.0,
      "end_time": 289260.0,
      "text": "the small digital warhead"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 289260.0,
      "end_time": 291260.0,
      "text": "with the rotor control."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 291260.0,
      "end_time": 294260.0,
      "text": "The rotor is that moving part within the centrifuge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 294260.0,
      "end_time": 296260.0,
      "text": "that black object that you see."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 296260.0,
      "end_time": 299260.0,
      "text": "And if you manipulate the speed of this rotor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 299260.0,
      "end_time": 301260.0,
      "text": "you are actually able to crack the rotor"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 301260.0,
      "end_time": 305260.0,
      "text": "and eventually even have the centrifuge explode."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 305260.0,
      "end_time": 307260.0,
      "text": "What we also saw"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 307260.0,
      "end_time": 309260.0,
      "text": "is that the goal of the attack"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 309260.0,
      "end_time": 312260.0,
      "text": "was really to do it slowly and creepy --"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 312260.0,
      "end_time": 314260.0,
      "text": "obviously in an effort"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 314260.0,
      "end_time": 317260.0,
      "text": "to drive maintenance engineers crazy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 317260.0,
      "end_time": 320260.0,
      "text": "that they would not be able to figure this out quickly."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 320260.0,
      "end_time": 323260.0,
      "text": "The big digital warhead -- we had a shot at this"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 323260.0,
      "end_time": 325260.0,
      "text": "by looking very closely"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 325260.0,
      "end_time": 327260.0,
      "text": "at data and data structures."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 327260.0,
      "end_time": 329260.0,
      "text": "So for example, the number 164"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 329260.0,
      "end_time": 331260.0,
      "text": "really stands out in that code;"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 331260.0,
      "end_time": 333260.0,
      "text": "you can&#39;t overlook it."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 333260.0,
      "end_time": 335260.0,
      "text": "I started to research scientific literature"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 335260.0,
      "end_time": 337260.0,
      "text": "on how these centrifuges"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 337260.0,
      "end_time": 339260.0,
      "text": "are actually built in Natanz"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 339260.0,
      "end_time": 341260.0,
      "text": "and found they are structured"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 341260.0,
      "end_time": 343260.0,
      "text": "in what is called a cascade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 343260.0,
      "end_time": 347260.0,
      "text": "and each cascade holds 164 centrifuges."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 347260.0,
      "end_time": 349260.0,
      "text": "So that made sense, that was a match."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 349260.0,
      "end_time": 351260.0,
      "text": "And it even got better."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 351260.0,
      "end_time": 353260.0,
      "text": "These centrifuges in Iran"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 353260.0,
      "end_time": 357260.0,
      "text": "are subdivided into 15, what is called, stages."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 357260.0,
      "end_time": 359260.0,
      "text": "And guess what we found in the attack code?"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 359260.0,
      "end_time": 361260.0,
      "text": "An almost identical structure."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 361260.0,
      "end_time": 364260.0,
      "text": "So again, that was a real good match."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 364260.0,
      "end_time": 367260.0,
      "text": "And this gave us very high confidence for what we were looking at."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 367260.0,
      "end_time": 370260.0,
      "text": "Now don&#39;t get me wrong here, it didn&#39;t go like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 370260.0,
      "end_time": 373260.0,
      "text": "These results have been obtained"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 373260.0,
      "end_time": 376260.0,
      "text": "over several weeks of really hard labor."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 376260.0,
      "end_time": 379260.0,
      "text": "And we often went into just a dead end"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 379260.0,
      "end_time": 381260.0,
      "text": "and had to recover."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 381260.0,
      "end_time": 383260.0,
      "text": "Anyway, so we figured out"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 383260.0,
      "end_time": 385260.0,
      "text": "that both digital warheads"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 385260.0,
      "end_time": 387260.0,
      "text": "were actually aiming at one and the same target,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 387260.0,
      "end_time": 389260.0,
      "text": "but from different angles."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 389260.0,
      "end_time": 392260.0,
      "text": "The small warhead is taking one cascade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 392260.0,
      "end_time": 395260.0,
      "text": "and spinning up the rotors and slowing them down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 395260.0,
      "end_time": 397260.0,
      "text": "and the big warhead"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 397260.0,
      "end_time": 399260.0,
      "text": "is talking to six cascades"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 399260.0,
      "end_time": 401260.0,
      "text": "and manipulating valves."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 401260.0,
      "end_time": 403260.0,
      "text": "So in all, we are very confident"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 403260.0,
      "end_time": 405260.0,
      "text": "that we have actually determined what the target is."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 405260.0,
      "end_time": 408260.0,
      "text": "It is Natanz, and it is only Natanz."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 408260.0,
      "end_time": 410260.0,
      "text": "So we don&#39;t have to worry"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 410260.0,
      "end_time": 412260.0,
      "text": "that other targets"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 412260.0,
      "end_time": 414260.0,
      "text": "might be hit by Stuxnet."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 414260.0,
      "end_time": 417260.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s some very cool stuff that we saw --"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 417260.0,
      "end_time": 419260.0,
      "text": "really knocked my socks off."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 419260.0,
      "end_time": 421260.0,
      "text": "Down there is the gray box,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 421260.0,
      "end_time": 424260.0,
      "text": "and on the top you see the centrifuges."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 424260.0,
      "end_time": 426260.0,
      "text": "Now what this thing does"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 426260.0,
      "end_time": 429260.0,
      "text": "is it intercepts the input values from sensors --"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 429260.0,
      "end_time": 431260.0,
      "text": "so for example, from pressure sensors"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 431260.0,
      "end_time": 433260.0,
      "text": "and vibration sensors --"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 433260.0,
      "end_time": 436260.0,
      "text": "and it provides legitimate program code,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 436260.0,
      "end_time": 438260.0,
      "text": "which is still running during the attack,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 438260.0,
      "end_time": 440260.0,
      "text": "with fake input data."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 440260.0,
      "end_time": 442260.0,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, this fake input data"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 442260.0,
      "end_time": 445260.0,
      "text": "is actually prerecorded by Stuxnet."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 445260.0,
      "end_time": 447260.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s just like from the Hollywood movies"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 447260.0,
      "end_time": 449260.0,
      "text": "where during the heist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 449260.0,
      "end_time": 452260.0,
      "text": "the observation camera is fed with prerecorded video."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 452260.0,
      "end_time": 454260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s cool, huh?"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 455260.0,
      "end_time": 457260.0,
      "text": "The idea here is obviously"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 457260.0,
      "end_time": 460260.0,
      "text": "not only to fool the operators in the control room."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 460260.0,
      "end_time": 464260.0,
      "text": "It actually is much more dangerous and aggressive."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 464260.0,
      "end_time": 466260.0,
      "text": "The idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 466260.0,
      "end_time": 469260.0,
      "text": "is to circumvent a digital safety system."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 470260.0,
      "end_time": 472260.0,
      "text": "We need digital safety systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 472260.0,
      "end_time": 475260.0,
      "text": "where a human operator could not act quick enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 475260.0,
      "end_time": 477260.0,
      "text": "So for example, in a power plant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 477260.0,
      "end_time": 480260.0,
      "text": "when your big steam turbine gets too over speed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 480260.0,
      "end_time": 483260.0,
      "text": "you must open relief valves within a millisecond."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 483260.0,
      "end_time": 486260.0,
      "text": "Obviously, this cannot be done by a human operator."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 486260.0,
      "end_time": 488260.0,
      "text": "So this is where we need digital safety systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 488260.0,
      "end_time": 490260.0,
      "text": "And when they are compromised,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 490260.0,
      "end_time": 493260.0,
      "text": "then real bad things can happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 493260.0,
      "end_time": 495260.0,
      "text": "Your plant can blow up."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 495260.0,
      "end_time": 498260.0,
      "text": "And neither your operators nor your safety system will notice it."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 498260.0,
      "end_time": 500260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s scary."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 500260.0,
      "end_time": 502260.0,
      "text": "But it gets worse."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 502260.0,
      "end_time": 505260.0,
      "text": "And this is very important, what I&#39;m going to say."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 505260.0,
      "end_time": 507260.0,
      "text": "Think about this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 507260.0,
      "end_time": 510260.0,
      "text": "this attack is generic."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 510260.0,
      "end_time": 514260.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t have anything to do, in specifics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 514260.0,
      "end_time": 516260.0,
      "text": "with centrifuges,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 516260.0,
      "end_time": 519260.0,
      "text": "with uranium enrichment."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 519260.0,
      "end_time": 522260.0,
      "text": "So it would work as well, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 522260.0,
      "end_time": 524260.0,
      "text": "in a power plant"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 524260.0,
      "end_time": 527260.0,
      "text": "or in an automobile factory."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 527260.0,
      "end_time": 529260.0,
      "text": "It is generic."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 529260.0,
      "end_time": 531260.0,
      "text": "And you don&#39;t have -- as an attacker --"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 531260.0,
      "end_time": 534260.0,
      "text": "you don&#39;t have to deliver this payload"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 534260.0,
      "end_time": 536260.0,
      "text": "by a USB stick,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 536260.0,
      "end_time": 538260.0,
      "text": "as we saw it in the case of Stuxnet."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 538260.0,
      "end_time": 541260.0,
      "text": "You could also use conventional worm technology for spreading."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 541260.0,
      "end_time": 544260.0,
      "text": "Just spread it as wide as possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 544260.0,
      "end_time": 546260.0,
      "text": "And if you do that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 546260.0,
      "end_time": 548260.0,
      "text": "what you end up with"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 548260.0,
      "end_time": 553260.0,
      "text": "is a cyber weapon of mass destruction."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 554260.0,
      "end_time": 556260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the consequence"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 556260.0,
      "end_time": 559260.0,
      "text": "that we have to face."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 559260.0,
      "end_time": 562260.0,
      "text": "So unfortunately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 562260.0,
      "end_time": 565260.0,
      "text": "the biggest number of targets for such attacks"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 565260.0,
      "end_time": 567260.0,
      "text": "are not in the Middle East."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 567260.0,
      "end_time": 570260.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re in the United States and Europe and in Japan."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 570260.0,
      "end_time": 572260.0,
      "text": "So all of the green areas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 572260.0,
      "end_time": 575260.0,
      "text": "these are your target-rich environments."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 575260.0,
      "end_time": 578260.0,
      "text": "We have to face the consequences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 578260.0,
      "end_time": 581260.0,
      "text": "and we better start to prepare right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 581260.0,
      "end_time": 583260.0,
      "text": "Thanks."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 583260.0,
      "end_time": 589260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 589260.0,
      "end_time": 591260.0,
      "text": "Chris Anderson: I&#39;ve got a question."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 593260.0,
      "end_time": 595260.0,
      "text": "Ralph, it&#39;s been quite widely reported"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 595260.0,
      "end_time": 597260.0,
      "text": "that people assume that Mossad"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 597260.0,
      "end_time": 599260.0,
      "text": "is the main entity behind this."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 599260.0,
      "end_time": 602260.0,
      "text": "Is that your opinion?"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 602260.0,
      "end_time": 604260.0,
      "text": "Ralph Langner: Okay, you really want to hear that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 604260.0,
      "end_time": 606260.0,
      "text": "Yeah. Okay."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 606260.0,
      "end_time": 609260.0,
      "text": "My opinion is that the Mossad is involved,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 609260.0,
      "end_time": 612260.0,
      "text": "but that the leading force is not Israel."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 612260.0,
      "end_time": 614260.0,
      "text": "So the leading force behind that"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 614260.0,
      "end_time": 617260.0,
      "text": "is the cyber superpower."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 617260.0,
      "end_time": 619260.0,
      "text": "There is only one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 619260.0,
      "end_time": 621260.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s the United States --"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 621260.0,
      "end_time": 623260.0,
      "text": "fortunately, fortunately."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 623260.0,
      "end_time": 625260.0,
      "text": "Because otherwise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 625260.0,
      "end_time": 628260.0,
      "text": "our problems would even be bigger."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 628260.0,
      "end_time": 632260.0,
      "text": "CA: Thank you for scaring the living daylights out of us. Thank you, Ralph."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 632260.0,
      "end_time": 634260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}